text: Hondret bischoc gief on hondred dage.
Porte bischop on hondreid dage and bihet þrou hondreit dage.
Leueger bischop bihet to hondreit dage.
Eadberht bischop biget frou hondreit dage, and tin dage.
Eansberht bischop biget sonne hondreit dage.
Ealnod bischop biget and hondreit dage.
Alger bischop bihet þru hondreit dage and souenti and þru dages.
Luhing bischop to hondreit dage, and on oþer leon popa hit ivasnede on echenisse ant aywilday.
